thread.title: Trump blocks release of Democrats' Russia memo

title: Trump blocks release of Democrats' Russia memo
text:
Trump blocks release of Democrats' Russia memo 9:33pm IST - 01:15 
President Donald Trump on Friday blocked the release of a classified memo written by congressional Democrats to rebut a Republican document that he allowed to be made public last week that claimed FBI and Justice Department bias against him in the federal probe of Russia and the 2016 U.S. election. Nathan Frandino reports.
